===Verb===
{{en-verb|'''[[speaks]]''' ''or {{qualifier|archaic}}'' '''[[speaketh]]'''|speaking|'''[[spoke]]''' ''or {{qualifier|archaic}}'' '''[[spake]]'''|spoken}}
